title: Ep.17: Burrow and Chase, Packers Clinch #1, Antonio Brown, Georgia vs Alabama, Playoff picture, and More!
description: It was a wild weekend, nothing more wild than AB walking out mid-game. Joe Burrow and Jamarr Chase are putting up insane numbers. The Packers starters have about 3 weeks off, how will that affect them? Tune in for more!
dc:creator: Griffin Proctor & Joe Jokonya
